ken, we are not\r\nresponsible for viruses, trojans, worms that could affect the\r\nend-user after entering the site or upon any transfer or load to or\r\nfrom the site.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;We\r\ncan not be charged with any claim or request for compensation of any\r\nkind.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14pt&quot; size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Modification\r\nof this agreement &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;This\r\nAgreement may be amended at any time and without notice to the end\r\nuser. Although the changes made will be notified through the website\r\nor through email, any modifications can be made at any time.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14pt&quot; size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Purchasing\r\n&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;All\r\npurchases made on the site shall be made on the understanding that\r\nthe information provided must be complete, this means, it must\r\ncontain all information necessary for the delivery of products can be\r\ndone. We are not responsible for lost items in shipping in case that\r\nthe information provided by the user, such as the shipping address is\r\nincomplete or wrong. The user may not under any circumstances\r\nmanipulate the price of the goods, if a change is found we will\r\ncancel your account and will take legal action.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt